  <brief_title>Counseling During Pulmonary Rehabilitation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Counseling During Pulmonary Rehabilitation on Self-determined Motivation Towards Physical Activity in Patients With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease</official_title>
