  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate if a physical activity counseling program during
      pulmonary rehabilitation increases the physical activity level in daily life in patients with
      Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
